The '''Starlight Theater''' was an ampitheatre on [[Phyrstal Island]] in the resort city of [[Le Yer]] on the planet [[Abregado-rae/Legends|Abregado-rae]]. It saw many performers take the stage. [[Yorl Niba]] and [[Brinaloy N'Vaari]] were two such performers, although a rivalry formed when Brinaloy attracted larger audiences.

